    The following additional schemas are defined:

    population_ID as attribute of each unit
    <epoch ...>
      <unit id=... [type="{1|2|3|4}"]>
        -36.7667 -36.0667 -35.0000 -33.5333 ... 
      </unit>
    </epoch>
